Products
Featured Products
To look for a product :

Québec Agri-Food Export Group  – Product Search (Partner of us, the Ministry of Agriculture, Fisheries and Foods of Québec – MAPAQ)
Carrefour alimentaire

Ice Cider
Award-winning and critically-acclaimed, ice cider is an alcoholic beverage produced from a select blend of hand-picked apples, harvested after frost and extracted naturally over the winter months. The unique combination of ideal summer growing conditions and cold Canadian winters create a product like nothing you have ever tasted!
This well kept secret is no more, as this delicious beverage is now exported to more than 20 countries in Europe and Asia, as well as in the United States.

Berries
Berries… cranberries, strawberries, raspberries, and blueberries, fragrant, sweet, and tangy. In Québec, we are as fond of them as we are of our traditions. Despite the temptation to eat them all straight from the farm, Québec is a leading supplier of processed products derived from berries, ranging from dried sweetened products to concentrates to IQF fruit.

Maple Syrup
Did you know that Québec produces more than 80 percent of the world’s maple syrup? This natural, nutritious product comes from the sap of the sugar maple tree and is produced through the evaporation of maple water. It takes 40 gallons of maple water to produce 1 gallon of maple syrup.
Did you know that maple syrup has many flavor profiles? Generally speaking, the lighter the color grade, the more delicate the flavor and the darker the color grade, the stronger the taste. These flavors are heavily influenced by the « terroir » or growing regions of the sugar maple trees and can give maple syrup a range of taste from traditional maple to vanilla or fruity… the possibilities are endless.
More than just another traditional product, maple syrup is one of the cultural food ingredients associated with Quebecers. From the provinces origins to today,  maple syrup remains a star ingredient in Québec and international cooking in the 21st century. Maple from Québec is available in a variety of traditional and innovative forms such as sugars, chips, whipped creamy maple, maple vinegar, maple flakes, maple pearls and much more!
















Buy wine, alcohols and spirits in-store and online | SAQ.com
























































